[
  {
    "startTime": 0.0,
    "endTime": 1.0,
    "text": "Happy birthday!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 1.0,
    "endTime": 3.0,
    "text": "Come on, Granny George, there are a bunch of candles."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 3.0,
    "endTime": 6.0,
    "text": "Yeah, I prefer my phase medium rare, not char-grilled."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 6.0,
    "endTime": 7.0,
    "text": "Why are there so many candles?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 7.0,
    "endTime": 8.0,
    "text": "I'm only 63."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 8.0,
    "endTime": 11.0,
    "text": "Sorry, we didn't know exactly how old you were, so we based it on looks."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 11.0,
    "endTime": 13.0,
    "text": "Do you need some help blowing them out?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 13.0,
    "endTime": 14.0,
    "text": "Kid, I raised your dad by myself."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 14.0,
    "endTime": 17.0,
    "text": "It's not the first time I've had to put out a fire."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 17.0,
    "endTime": 24.0,
    "text": "I think it's time for a toast."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 24.0,
    "endTime": 27.0,
    "text": "Thank you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 27.0,
    "endTime": 30.0,
    "text": "And now for your birthday surprise."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 30.0,
    "endTime": 33.0,
    "text": "The alphabet of my mom."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 33.0,
    "endTime": 35.0,
    "text": "A is for amazing, because that's what you are."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 35.0,
    "endTime": 38.0,
    "text": "B is for breakfast, one of my 12 favorite mealtimes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 38.0,
    "endTime": 40.0,
    "text": "And because you're amazing, Mom."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 40.0,
    "endTime": 44.0,
    "text": "Nicole, I just wanted to say that you look really average today."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 44.0,
    "endTime": 44.0,
    "text": "Oh, yeah?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 44.0,
    "endTime": 47.0,
    "text": "Well, you look like someone drew an ugly face on a butt with a..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 47.0,
    "endTime": 47.0,
    "text": "Wait, what?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 47.0,
    "endTime": 48.0,
    "text": "Did you just say average?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 48.0,
    "endTime": 51.0,
    "text": "That's got to be the least offensive thing you've ever said to me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 51.0,
    "endTime": 52.0,
    "text": "Do you need a lie-down?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 52.0,
    "endTime": 54.0,
    "text": "Yeah, and you gave us real candy instead of your expired fungus medication."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 54.0,
    "endTime": 56.0,
    "text": "And your face looks wrong."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 56.0,
    "endTime": 58.0,
    "text": "It's like your mouth is upside down."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 58.0,
    "endTime": 59.0,
    "text": "It's almost as if you are smiling."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 59.0,
    "endTime": 59.0,
    "text": "Why?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 59.0,
    "endTime": 62.0,
    "text": "Because I like them."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 62.0,
    "endTime": 68.0,
    "text": "And Z is for zebra, an amazing mythical creature, but not as amazing as you, Mom."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 68.0,
    "endTime": 69.0,
    "text": "Thank you, Richard."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 69.0,
    "endTime": 71.0,
    "text": "Like every year, that was a nice surprise."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 71.0,
    "endTime": 74.0,
    "text": "And while we're on the topic, I also have a surprise for all of you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 74.0,
    "endTime": 74.0,
    "text": "Surprise!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 74.0,
    "endTime": 77.0,
    "text": "Sorry, sir."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 77.0,
    "endTime": 79.0,
    "text": "We already got a surprise here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 79.0,
    "endTime": 80.0,
    "text": "We don't need any more."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 80.0,
    "endTime": 81.0,
    "text": "Nice to meet you, sir."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 81.0,
    "endTime": 83.0,
    "text": "This is Louie."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 83.0,
    "endTime": 84.0,
    "text": "He's my boyfriend."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 84.0,
    "endTime": 84.0,
    "text": "Huh?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 84.0,
    "endTime": 98.0,
    "text": "Dear, are you all right?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 98.0,
    "endTime": 99.0,
    "text": "What's with the voice?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 99.0,
    "endTime": 100.0,
    "text": "I don't know."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 100.0,
    "endTime": 102.0,
    "text": "It just felt appropriate."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 102.0,
    "endTime": 104.0,
    "text": "Dad, wake up!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 104.0,
    "endTime": 105.0,
    "text": "Get the first aid kit."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 105.0,
    "endTime": 105.0,
    "text": "Clear!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 105.0,
    "endTime": 111.0,
    "text": "That's so much in common."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 111.0,
    "endTime": 114.0,
    "text": "I can't wait till we get there."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 114.0,
    "endTime": 116.0,
    "text": "If you have something to say, then you should share it with the whole family."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 116.0,
    "endTime": 119.0,
    "text": "To be honest with you, I have no idea what he said."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 119.0,
    "endTime": 121.0,
    "text": "My hearing isn't what it used to be."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 121.0,
    "endTime": 121.0,
    "text": "Me neither."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 121.0,
    "endTime": 123.0,
    "text": "I was just laughing and hoping it wasn't a question."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 123.0,
    "endTime": 127.0,
    "text": "We've got so much in common."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 127.0,
    "endTime": 129.0,
    "text": "Yeah, we're both falling apart."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 129.0,
    "endTime": 136.0,
    "text": "So, Louie, what career plans do you have?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 136.0,
    "endTime": 137.0,
    "text": "None."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 137.0,
    "endTime": 140.0,
    "text": "He's got no prospects."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 140.0,
    "endTime": 141.0,
    "text": "Actually, I'm retired."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 141.0,
    "endTime": 142.0,
    "text": "Come on, Nicole."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 142.0,
    "endTime": 144.0,
    "text": "Laugh at him with me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 144.0,
    "endTime": 146.0,
    "text": "Come on, kids."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 146.0,
    "endTime": 148.0,
    "text": "Say something mean and ironic about him."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 148.0,
    "endTime": 148.0,
    "text": "No?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 148.0,
    "endTime": 148.0,
    "text": "Fine."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 149.0,
    "endTime": 151.0,
    "text": "I'll do it myself."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 151.0,
    "endTime": 152.0,
    "text": "Where did you retire from?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 152.0,
    "endTime": 153.0,
    "text": "Santa's factory?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 153.0,
    "endTime": 154.0,
    "text": "Because you're small!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 154.0,
    "endTime": 154.0,
    "text": "Burn!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 154.0,
    "endTime": 161.0,
    "text": "Why did you steal my mom?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 161.0,
    "endTime": 166.0,
    "text": "Is it me, or is the atmosphere a little heavy?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 166.0,
    "endTime": 169.0,
    "text": "Well, that was very nice."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 169.0,
    "endTime": 171.0,
    "text": "Catch you later, cottontail."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 171.0,
    "endTime": 176.0,
    "text": "Get out of my house!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 176.0,
    "endTime": 178.0,
    "text": "Uh, he just did."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 178.0,
    "endTime": 182.0,
    "text": "Now get out of my house!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 182.0,
    "endTime": 183.0,
    "text": "You're the one who dragged me back here, son."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 183.0,
    "endTime": 185.0,
    "text": "Call me son one more time!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 185.0,
    "endTime": 186.0,
    "text": "I dare you!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 186.0,
    "endTime": 187.0,
    "text": "I double dare you!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 187.0,
    "endTime": 188.0,
    "text": "You mother-robber!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 188.0,
    "endTime": 189.0,
    "text": "Kids, come over here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 189.0,
    "endTime": 191.0,
    "text": "Okay, you grab this arm."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 191.0,
    "endTime": 192.0,
    "text": "Now you take my leg."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 192.0,
    "endTime": 193.0,
    "text": "Let me at him!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 193.0,
    "endTime": 194.0,
    "text": "Let me at him!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 194.0,
    "endTime": 198.0,
    "text": "You're lucky they're here, or you'd end up in a mobility scooter for the rest of your life!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 198.0,
    "endTime": 200.0,
    "text": "Let me at him!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 200.0,
    "endTime": 200.0,
    "text": "That's right!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 200.0,
    "endTime": 200.0,
    "text": "Faster!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 201.0,
    "endTime": 203.0,
    "text": "Faster, old man!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 204.0,
    "endTime": 208.0,
    "text": "I'm trying, but this thing takes 20 minutes to go from zero to eight miles an hour."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 208.0,
    "endTime": 213.0,
    "text": "What is father gonna say when he comes back?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 213.0,
    "endTime": 213.0,
    "text": "Father?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 213.0,
    "endTime": 214.0,
    "text": "Yeah!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 214.0,
    "endTime": 217.0,
    "text": "You said he left to buy some milk 42 years ago."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 217.0,
    "endTime": 218.0,
    "text": " He could be back any minute!"
  }
]